data.title: 102 Robbins Circle, Dennis, MA 02638
data.meta_description: 102 Robbins Circle, Dennis, MA 02638 is pending. Zillow has 65 photos of this 3 beds, 3 baths, 2,509 Square Feet single family home with a list price of $1,250,000.
data.text: This move in ready charmer offers hard to find privacy overlooking lush lawns and mature greenery. Yet located in a delightful neighborhood within a short walk to both Dennis Village and GORGEOUS Mayflower Beach. Absolutely turnkey, this home has been completely redone with top-of-the-line improvements. Featuring a pretty living/dining room with large fireplace, gleaming hardwood floors, a splashy new kitchen with terrific center island, stainless Viking & Thermador appliances, & sliders to a huge new TREK deck overlooking the beautiful grounds. And a first-floor bedroom, remodeled half bath and laundry. Upstairs find two more bedrooms and terrific new bathroom with large walk-in shower. Need more? The lower level is nicely finished with room for overflow, office, or family room. Then stroll out to a fabulous, screened porch which is perfect for those balmy summer evenings. This rare 2-acre lot offers privacy but little upkeep in the Heart of Dennis. All of this and being sold fully furnished! Move right in and head to Mayflower Beach just down the street. There's even room for a pool. Nothing to do but enjoy!
